  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the efficacy of predilation with paclitaxel-eluting
      balloon and bare metal stent implantation VS conventional balloon and drug-eluting stent
      implantation in terms of restenosis
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Terminated</overall_status>
  <why_stopped>
    the study was halted after an interim analysis perfomed for a perceived excess of target vessel
    revascularization in the DEB+BMS arm
  </why_stopped>
